text: Amica Hallendorff (born 26 October 1992) is a South African water polo player. She competed for the South Africa women's national water polo team in the 2015 World Aquatics Championships, 2017 World Aquatics Championships, and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * amica- hallendorff swimswam * 2017 Hallendorff amica RSA player alamy Category:1992 births Category:South African water polo players Category:Living people
